    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Primary validation result demonstrates NIH predictions within 11.8% of bench measurements across all operating points with RH < 1 satisfied. Assurance level recorded as High per sponsor directive. The secondary shear-stress validation result provides supporting qualitative evidence consistent with hemolysis mechanism literature. Overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
